### Rotating Savings

A web-based application designed to manage rotating savings groups in a structured and transparent way.
The platform centralizes payout schedules, payout order, and payment tracking into one organized system,
 eliminating confusion caused by managing savings through chat platforms.

### Features
    User registration and authentication
    Secure login & logout
    Create and join savings groups
    Automatic random payout order generation
    Payout schedule display
    Payment tracking (Paid / Unpaid status)
    Upload payment proof (image screenshots)
    User dashboard displaying group activity
    Session management using Flask-Login

### System Architecture
    The application follows the MVC (Model–View–Controller) design pattern:
    Models → Database structure using Flask-SQLAlchemy
    Views → HTML templates rendered with Jinja2
    Controllers → Flask routes handling business logic
    Authentication Layer → Flask-Login manages user sessions

